100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"保就業」計劃秘書處今日（七月六日）在「保就業」計劃網站（<a href=\"http://www.ess.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ess.gov.hk&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=8acc6478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.ess.gov.hk</a>）公布第三批已領取工資補貼的僱主名單、補貼金額及承諾受薪僱員人數。<br />\n <br />\n　　政府發言人表示：「『保就業』計劃秘書處於六月二十二日及二十九日分別公布了兩批領取工資補貼的僱主名單。今天公布的第三批僱主名單，涉及約30 000名僱主，工資補貼額合共約77億元（二○二○年六月至八月），有關僱主承諾於補貼期內維持超過33萬名受薪僱員。」<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，「保就業」計劃秘書處亦於今日開始向第四批約11 000名成功申請僱主發放工資補貼，涉及的補貼額約63億元，承諾受薪僱員人數約270 000。秘書處會在完成發放該批工資補貼後公布有關僱主名單。秘書處亦將會向第四批約一萬名自僱人士發放7,500元的一次過資助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/06/P2020070600244.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F06%2FP2020070600244.htm&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=782e8f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/06/P2020070600244.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200706/mobile/bkn-20200706112043999-0706_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200706%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200706112043999-0706_00822_001.html&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FrktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=a2072989\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200706/mobile/bkn-20200706112043999-0706_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200706/photo/bkn-20200706112043999-0706_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200706134728\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200706%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200706112043999-0706_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200706134728&h=83fe9ec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a64142b3bc5b83fbef651c78e1f9c6e50ff7cbbe","tid":2096393,"uid":23104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://6